<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.9.4">
<l>malkiya tōḷum māṉuri yataḷu muṭaiyavar tamakkumōr pākam</l>
<l>nalkiya nalamō narakaṉai tolaitta karatalat tamaitiyiṉ karuttō</l>
<l>valliyaṅ kōtai yaṇiniṟam koṇṭu vantumuṉ ṉēniṉṟu pōkāy</l>
<l>colliyeṉ nampī yivaḷainī yuṅkaḷ toṇṭarkait taṇṭeṉṟa vāṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it [your] goodness that bestowed a part of yourself to him</l>
<l rend="indent">with an elephant hide skin and many arms?</l>
<l>Is it the thought of the nature of the hands that killed Naraka?</l>
<l rend="indent">[Thus] you do not leave [her thoughts],</l>
<l rend="indent">remaining before [her mind’s eye],</l>
<l>Having come stealing the lovely complexion of my lily-adorned girl.</l>
<l>What [is the use of] talking, prince? Oh, the way that you think her a staff</l>
<l rend="indent">in your servant’s hand!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
